My newsboat is configured to use w3m (a textonly browser) as default browser
browser &#34;w3m %u&#34; from times to times you enconter some pages that does not look good on text-only browser , this config defines a macro to open the default browser by pressing ,m (COMMA + lowercase m)
macro m set browser &#34;xdg-open %u&#34;; open-in-browser ; set browser &#34;w3m %u&#34;
